snippet.title: Wildlife Videos
snippet.description:
Welcome to Wildlife Videos

Dear all Viewers!   Glad to come to my channel. I created this channel because I love the scenery, nature and animals and  I always get up early in the morning and go to the market to buy fruits for them to eat. I have no money, but I try to buy and to feed them, because I feel sorry for them, living there helpless, there is no food to find.  Please support and love these animals, please subscribe and recommend your friends to join me, I will continue to do it and to buy fruits to feed them.
There are various monkeys here since a long time Monkeys, and Newborn youngster monkeys are dazzling to be engaging for close by visit. 
We endeavor to film for you and extraordinary movement the whole of the animals,
 
Let me know about your thoughts sending an email to: sr.samoun@gmail.com

I'd love for you to subscribe and join our great community!
thanks, all guys for good idea and comments I would love all 
Best Regard,
